      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver. While the engine and transmission are functional and the car remains roadworthy, it does show noticeable signs of use, including some minor exterior cosmetic blemishes and interior wear on the upholstery. It has been maintained to keep it running safely, though a buyer should expect the typical character of a well-used vehicle. This is a great choice for someone looking for a dependable car at an affordable price point.",
