      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering a superior balance of performance and refined aesthetics. This unit exhibits a documented history of consistent care, resulting in a driving experience that remains sharp and responsive. The interior and exterior have been preserved to a high standard, ensuring an executive presence on the road. For the discerning buyer seeking a reliable, high-value asset, this vehicle represents an optimal acquisition.",
      "price": 36800.0,
